url

/api/v1/auth/signup             -----> Signup
/api/v1/auth/login              -----> Login
/api/v1/auth/password-reset     -----> passwordreset


/api/v1/user/:id   -----> GetUserDetails
/api/v1/user/:id   -----> CreateUserDetails
/api/v1/user/:id   -----> UpdateUserDetails
/api/v1/user/:id   -----> DeleteUserDetails




